550
00:42:38,094 --> 00:42:40,204
There, there, Ton.

551
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:45,200
Getting told off by the
village chief's daughter.

552
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:53,500
Just ignore them.

553
00:42:53,666 --> 00:42:55,966
Is there somewhere we can talk?

554
00:42:57,366 --> 00:42:58,866
My room. It's on the third floor.

555
00:42:59,266 --> 00:43:00,300
Oh, perfect.

556
00:43:00,566 --> 00:43:01,933
I brought you something.

557
00:43:02,166 --> 00:43:04,166
We can talk upstairs later.

558
00:43:13,166 --> 00:43:17,003
Just so you know, Erng is mine.

559
00:43:18,765 --> 00:43:20,512
What do you mean "mine," Hia?

560
00:43:26,266 --> 00:43:27,266
You jerk.

561
00:43:27,666 --> 00:43:28,666
Ton.

562
00:43:30,970 --> 00:43:31,970
It's okay.

563
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:41,239
Hia.

564
00:43:42,600 --> 00:43:44,802
I'm hungry. Can you go
buy me some noodle soup?

565
00:43:45,034 --> 00:43:46,338
From the place at the end of the street.

566
00:43:46,339 --> 00:43:50,932
Get two orders with extra crispy pork.
One for me and one for Chon.

567
00:43:51,466 --> 00:43:53,000
But if you want some too...

568
00:43:53,733 --> 00:43:54,853
You'll have to buy your own.

569
00:43:55,400 --> 00:43:57,666
I only have a hundred baht.

570
00:44:01,466 --> 00:44:02,966
Why don't you ever treat me?

571
00:44:03,600 --> 00:44:05,600
Let your man treat you.

572
00:44:06,366 --> 00:44:07,366
Here.

573
00:44:08,666 --> 00:44:09,733
And while you're at it...

574
00:44:09,866 --> 00:44:11,466
Fill up the motorcycle with gas, too.

575
00:44:11,966 --> 00:44:13,806
You're really taking
advantage of me now, huh?

576
00:44:13,866 --> 00:44:14,866
Where's the money?

577
00:44:15,266 --> 00:44:16,066
I don't have any.

578
00:44:16,200 --> 00:44:17,640
I'm not running, but I'm not paying.

579
00:44:18,266 --> 00:44:19,909
If you don't fill it up by this evening...

580
00:44:19,933 --> 00:44:21,733
You can just take the Benz to the market.

581
00:44:23,566 --> 00:44:25,942
Ton, what's wrong with the bike? [A Thai
meme]

582
00:44:25,966 --> 00:44:27,600
Oh, it won't start.

583
00:44:28,133 --> 00:44:29,133
Put some gas in it.

584
00:44:29,300 --> 00:44:30,933
So it'll be good and start easily.

585
00:44:33,566 --> 00:44:34,733
My friend has changed.

586
00:44:35,100 --> 00:44:36,100
No more talk.

587
00:44:36,166 --> 00:44:37,376
I have to hurry to the end of the street.

588
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:39,066
My beloved wants his special noodle soup.

589
00:44:39,133 --> 00:44:40,253
Two orders with crispy pork.

590
00:44:40,800 --> 00:44:41,800
He's craving it.

591
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:43,280
I have to go get it for him now.

592
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:45,866
Let my friend Ton
watch the shop for a bit.

593
00:44:47,100 --> 00:44:48,766
Yeah, just hurry back.

594
00:44:53,366 --> 00:44:54,533
Let's go, Chon.

595
00:44:54,900 --> 00:44:55,555
Let's get out of here.

596
00:44:55,556 --> 00:44:56,600
- Okay.
- Let's go.

597
00:45:16,466 --> 00:45:18,966
Hello? Nai? It's me, Ton.

598
00:45:29,588 --> 00:45:31,400
(Intha &amp; Ai Khem)

599
00:45:31,700 --> 00:45:33,748
I don't think this relationship is normal.

600
00:45:33,749 --> 00:45:37,661
Normal people start by going to the
movies, eating out, holding hands, right?

601
00:45:37,662 --> 00:45:40,811
But we started with my
ex storming into the shop.

602
00:45:40,812 --> 00:45:42,266
And Hia beat him half to death.

603
00:45:42,666 --> 00:45:43,800
Well, didn't he deserve it?

604
00:45:43,966 --> 00:45:45,806
Who told him he could
grab my boyfriend's arm?

605
00:45:45,933 --> 00:45:47,696
That's Intha.

606
00:45:47,697 --> 00:45:50,966
He's a man of few words, but he loves
saying things just to make my heart race.

607
00:45:52,000 --> 00:45:53,066
After that day,

608
00:45:53,766 --> 00:45:55,066
everything started to change.

609
00:45:56,266 --> 00:45:57,866
I started taking him to meet my friends.

610
00:45:58,600 --> 00:46:00,266
Bringing him into my world.

611
00:46:00,866 --> 00:46:02,700
I didn't think Hia would get that jealous.

612
00:46:03,066 --> 00:46:04,226
He even kicked the wrong guy.

613
00:46:04,566 --> 00:46:06,166
Well, everyone was getting close to you.

614
00:46:06,266 --> 00:46:07,826
How was I supposed to know who was who?

615
00:46:07,866 --> 00:46:09,766
I was so possessive I almost lost my mind.

616
00:46:10,200 --> 00:46:11,200
That's when I realized

617
00:46:11,533 --> 00:46:13,333
that a quiet guy like Hia In,

618
00:46:13,533 --> 00:46:14,966
when he gets hit by love,

619
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:17,166
he's even more childish than me.

620
00:46:17,167 --> 00:46:20,785
But the thing I remember
most is that sentence.

621
00:46:20,786 --> 00:46:21,800
Be my boyfriend.

622
00:46:23,266 --> 00:46:26,852
I never thought I'd be the
one to ask someone out first.

623
00:46:26,853 --> 00:46:30,168
But back then, I really
didn't want to lose Hia.

624
00:46:30,585 --> 00:46:33,054
Erng likes to say things
that make my heart drop,

625
00:46:33,471 --> 00:46:36,944
but in the end, he always chooses me.

626
00:46:41,000 --> 00:46:42,418
Ever since Hia In came into my life,

627
00:46:42,419 --> 00:46:44,724
my life has gotten a lot more chaotic.

628
00:46:44,725 --> 00:46:49,275
There's someone who's possessive,
scolds me, and drags me to take a shower.

629
00:46:49,276 --> 00:46:51,396
Someone who forces me to
wear matching couple shirts.

630
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,098
But it's strange.

631
00:46:53,099 --> 00:46:55,300
I'm so damn happy.

632
00:46:55,966 --> 00:46:57,437
I never thought that

633
00:46:57,438 --> 00:46:59,878
someone like me could
get so attached to anyone.

634
00:46:59,879 --> 00:47:01,599
When I see him smile, I just want to watch.

635
00:47:02,500 --> 00:47:04,460
When I see him quiet, I
want to ask what's wrong.

636
00:47:04,866 --> 00:47:07,300
Maybe love doesn't have to be perfect.

637
00:47:08,100 --> 00:47:09,933
Just having someone who still chooses you,

638
00:47:10,533 --> 00:47:12,213
even on the days you're totally unlovable,

639
00:47:12,533 --> 00:47:13,966
might really be enough.

640
00:47:15,100 --> 00:47:16,266
And from now on,

641
00:47:16,966 --> 00:47:18,566
there will probably be a lot more chaos.

642
00:47:18,800 --> 00:47:20,600
But as long as I have Erng by my side,

643
00:47:21,100 --> 00:47:22,966
I'm ready to face anything.

644
00:47:25,900 --> 00:47:27,780
(Next Episode)
Did you put a spell on my friend?

645
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:29,900
Black magic, you mean?

646
00:47:30,541 --> 00:47:31,341
What are you doing?

647
00:47:31,366 --> 00:47:33,700
Yeah, the love spell.

648
00:47:34,200 --> 00:47:35,200
I didn't do it.

649
00:47:35,500 --> 00:47:36,500
You didn't?

650
00:47:36,600 --> 00:47:38,333
Then why is my friend so crazy about you?
